/* Background Colors */
--color-background-light: #411f07;     /* Dark background */
--color-background-medium: #592b0a;   /* Card backgrounds */
--color-background-dark: #2a1504;     /* Subtle backgrounds */
```

### **Typography Hierarchy**

#### **Font Families**
- **Primary**: System fonts (San Francisco, Segoe UI, Roboto)
- **Game Title**: Custom font "KG Kiss Me Slowly" for branding
- **UI Elements**: System fonts for consistency

#### **Font Sizes**
